nmap <leader>ff <Action>(GotoFile)
"find grep
nmap <leader>fg <Action>(FindInPath)
"find fuzzy
nmap <leader>fz <Action>(Find)
"find in buffer
nmap <leader>fb <Action>(RecentFiles)
"find and replace
nmap <leader>fr <Action>(ReplaceInPath)

" todo --------------------------------------
