""" Movement ---------------------------------
nnoremap N Nzz
nnoremap n nzz
vnoremap N Nzz
vnoremap n nzz
nnoremap <C-u> <C-u>zz
nnoremap <C-d> <C-d>zz

" continuous shift
xnoremap < <gv
xnoremap > >gv

""" Commands ---------------------------------
command W w

